<data>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_start" type="sel">
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main" once="true">
            <text>"Hello, welcome to the Stratis Hotel. How can I be of assistance?"</text>
        </line>
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main">
            <text>"Welcome back. How can I be of assistance?"</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_main_return">
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main">
            <text>"Very well. Anything else I can do for you?"</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_main">
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_request_room">Do you have any rooms available?</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_info">I have some questions.</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_end">That will be all.</choice>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_request_room">
        <condition type="var">
            <variable>purchased_stratis_room</variable>
            <equality>EQUAL</equality>
            <value>0</value>
        </condition>
        <line>
            <text>He taps the screen in front of him and quickly scans its contents.</text>
            <text>"Yes, it appears we have an available room on the fifth floor. King bed, thirty-inch holoscreen, and a beautiful view of the commercial district. Only 300 credits a night."</text>
        </line>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_purchase_room" once="true">I'll take the room.</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_main_return">Not right now.</choice>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_purchase_room">
        <condition type="money">
            <actor target="player"/>
            <value>300</value>
        </condition>
        <line>
            <text>"Certainly. The room number is 508, on the fifth floor. You can use those elevators over there. Here's your keycard."</text>
            <text>He hands you a white keycard with the Stratis Hotel logo.</text>
            <script type="compound">
                <script type="addItem">
                    <actor target="player"/>
                    <item>stratis_room_key</item>
                </script>
                <script type="money">
                    <actor target="player"/>
                    <value>-300</value>
                </script>
                <script type="varSet">
                    <variable>purchased_stratis_room</variable>
                    <value>1</value>
                </script>
            </script>
        </line>
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main">
            <text>"Enjoy your stay. Is there anything else I can do for you?"</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_info">
        <line>
            <text>"Of course."</text>
        </line>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_info_amenities">What amenities are available here?</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_info_guests">Get a lot of high-profile guests here?</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_info_rees">Is there someone staying here by the name of Abel Rees?</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_combat">[Attack] Any last words?</choice>
        <choice link="stratis_receptionist_main_return">That's all.</choice>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_info_amenities">
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main">
            <text>The receptionist grins slightly.</text>
            <text>"Everything you could need. Five-star restaurant, rooftop pool."</text>
            <text>"We also provide the fastest network access of any hotel in the area, included with every room."</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_info_guests">
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main">
            <text>"Why yes, of course. The Stratis is the best, and most secure, hotel in the area."</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_info_rees">
        <line redirect="stratis_receptionist_main">
            <text>The receptionist narrows his eyes.</text>
            <text>"We can't disclose the identity of our guests to the public."</text>
            <text>"As you can imagine, that would be bad for business."</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_combat">
        <line exit="true">
            <text>The receptionist grits his teeth.</text>
            <text>"I don't give up that easily."</text>
            <script type="combat">
                <actor target="subject"/>
                <combatant target="player"/>
            </script>
        </line>
    </topic>
    <topic id="stratis_receptionist_end">
        <line exit="true">
            <text>"Very well. Have a lovely day."</text>
        </line>
    </topic>
</data>